            "title": "將貨就價！九龍客為享受樓價升軌及租金回報 「6球」轉買深井連租約兩房(有圖)｜二手樓成交",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"600\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/USswpVSSvf79r3JIUO5jKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/0de7f3363683223405ad8bc1a0314bb6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">600</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>二手交投氣氛向好，晉誠地產海韻分行高級經理李德鴻表示，分行新近促成深井<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"碧堤半島\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:碧堤半島;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/碧堤半島\">碧堤半島</a></span>1<span>期</span>8<span>座高層</span>F<span>室成交，單位實用面積約</span>524<span>方呎，兩房間隔，享山景，以</span>600<span>萬元連租約售出，呎價約</span>11,450<span>元。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>李德鴻透露，原業主一直將物業作收租之用，於今年</span>3<span>月開價</span>638<span>萬元連租約放售，最後獲買家議價</span>38<span>萬元或約</span>6%<span>承接。新買家於九龍區居住及工作，屬意於東九龍置業，奈何樓價不段攀升，想傾談的盤源又遇業主反價，偏離其買樓預算，最後決定轉區購入連租約物業，盡快享受樓價升軌及租金回報。</span></p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">⇊直擊<span>碧堤半島</span>1<span>期</span>8<span>座高層</span>F<span>室</span>⇊</h3><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span>原業主持貨</span>21<span>年帳賺近</span>1.8<span>倍</span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>據悉，原業主與關聯人士於</span>2005<span>年以</span>215<span>萬元購入單位，持貨約</span>21<span>年，現轉售帳面獲利</span>385<span>萬元，物業期內升值近</span>1.8<span>倍。</span></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8a932a7d-94d9-3943-80a4-fcac749d57d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>資料顯示，碧堤半島位於深井青山公路深井段</span>33<span>號，</span>2003<span>年入伙，分為</span>3<span>期共有</span>8<span>座，提供</span>3,345<span>伙。</span></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即睇深井碧堤半島放盤 (House730)\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即睇深井碧堤半島放盤 (House730);elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://bit.ly/3UwaPLB\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span><strong>即睇深井碧堤半島放盤</strong></span><strong> (House730)</strong></a></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/地產/1025744/將貨就價-九龍客為享受樓價升軌及租金回報-6球-轉買深井連租約兩房-有圖-二